              </div>
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-normal">
              Architected and delivered scalable, multi-tenant headless CMS
              solutions using Payload CMS and Next.js. Developed
              high-performance websites integrated with the Resemolnet SaaS
              booking system. Enhanced client SEO performance through dynamic
              structured content and metadata management. Built cross-platform
              mobile applications using React Native with Firebase integration.
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap" aria-label="Technologies used">
              <li class="mr-1.5 mt-2">
                <div
                  class="flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium leading-5 text-teal-300"
